#CircuitBreakerSG D-28
Good morning, we're at the halfway mark of our Circuit Breaker. Another 4 weeks to go 💪

Today we're having Avocado Egg Toast. Mash avocado 🥑 and season with ACV, garlic pepper & salt. Spread Avocado on grilled butter toast 🍞 and layer with scrambled egg 🍳. Serve with greens 🥗, Mandarin Orange 🍊 & must-have Coffee ☕ #NoMondayBlues

Stay home, eat well! Together we can fight the spread of Covid-19 🙏

😋 I like my Avocado slices with balsamic vinegar, black pepper & pink Himalayan salt, and maybe a drop of EVO if the 🥑 is a touch under !

Thank you for pledging to #StayHomeWithAscott. #CapitaLandHopeFoundation will be making a donation of US$10 to Save The Children and we look forward to more of your #StayHomeWithAscott posts. Stay home, stay safe and cook away!
Love your breakfast, so yummy 😋😍 And yes, we hv crosses the half way mark, we can do it together!!! 🦾🦾
